<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Ulm</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Auskunft wegen Anerkennung des Pfalzgrafen Ludwig III. als Reichsvikar.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_144" id="71v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_144_r2l1">Vlme </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_144_line_1572979727851_217"><expan>Lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> frewnde / Es ſind cʒü vns kumen <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>gnedige<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>H<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_144_r2l4">Ludwıgs <expan>Pfalcʒg<ex>ra</ex>fen</expan> bey Rein etc Rete her Hans von Erlıkem 
<add><ab facs="#facs_144_line_1572979731858_222"><expan>Rıtt<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab></add> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_144_r2l5"><expan>Joh<ex>an</ex></expan> <expan cert="unknown">kırch</expan> . mit <expan>ſeıne<ex>m</ex></expan> gelaubſbrief vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> an vns <expan>geworb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_144_r2l6">vvie derſelb vnſer <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Hercʒog / als <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> das Reıche yecʒund ledig </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_144_r2l7">ıſt / des Reıches fürſeher vnd vıcari ſeÿ / in diſen landen nach <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_144_r2l8">vnd er <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> in <expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> titel ſchreıbet / vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vns geſagt / vvie </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_144_r2l9">das an ew vnd die <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Stete <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> einung auch bracht ſeÿ / 
<del rend="strikethrough">vnd </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_144_r2l10">daʒ Jr Jn dafür <expan>halte<ex>n</ex></expan> ſolt / vnd das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Jm <expan>ein<ex>er</ex></expan> ewrs Rats <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_144_r2l11">Vlme vnd <expan>ein<ex>er</ex></expan> von <expan>heılprun<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd der <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Stete <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_144_r2l12">cʒügeſagt / . vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> darauf von vns begert / daʒ vvir Jn dafür </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_144_r2l13">auch <expan>halt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſüllen / Nu <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr vns beÿ <expan>diſe<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / ob </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_144_r2l14">vnd als vil das <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> vveiſheit füglıch ſeÿ / eigentlıch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_144_r2l15">wöllet / wie das an ew braht ſeÿ / vnd wie Jr vnd die <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Stete </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_144_r2l16">ſeinen gnaden / darauf <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> habt / Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir in </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_144_r2l17"><expan>ſolıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>ſach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> <expan>Sex<ex>ta</ex></expan> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>Mar<ex>ie</ex></expan> Magdalene / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_144" id="71v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Ulme </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> frewnde, es sind czü uns kumen
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedige<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan> Ludwigs,
                                <expan>pfalczg<ex>ra</ex>fen</expan> bey Rein etc., rete, her Hans
                        von Erlikem, <add><expan>ritt<ex>er</ex></expan></add>, und
                                <expan>Joh<ex>an</ex></expan>
<expan cert="unknown">Kirch<ex>ner</ex></expan>, mit
                            <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan> gelaubsbrief und
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> an uns <expan>geworb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>,
                        wie derselb unser <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>, <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        herczog, als <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> das reiche yeczund ledig ist, des
                        reiches fürseher und vicari sey in disen landen nach
                            <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> und er <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> in
                                <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan> titel schreibet; und
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns gesagt, wie das an ew und die
                                <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> stete <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        einung auch bracht sey, daz ir in dafür <expan>halte<ex>n</ex></expan> solt,
                        und das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> im <expan>ein<ex>er</ex></expan> ewrs
                        rats <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Ulme und <expan>ein<ex>er</ex></expan> von
                                <expan>Heilprun<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und der <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> stete
                                <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> czügesagt und
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> darauf von uns begert, daz wir in dafür
                        auch <expan>halt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> süllen. Nu
                            <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir uns bey
                            <expan>dise<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, ob und als vil das
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> weisheit füglich sey, eigentlich
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet, wie das an ew
                        braht sey und wie ir und die <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> stete seinen
                        gnaden darauf <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> habt. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir in
                            <expan>solich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan>
<expan>sex<ex>ta</ex></expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Mar<ex>ie</ex></expan> Magdalene.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
